result.description:
Issues observed are applied to all webpages in both websites:
- Need a link to skip navigation and jump to content;
- Landmark regions, such as header, footer, navigation, search and main content, need ARIA roles to allow quick navigation through keyboard;
- It's need to add a link at the beginning of a block of repeated content to go to the end of the block (such as lists);
- Some pages doesn't have heading or sub-heading.
